    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Magic action, you can reach into your Alchemist's Satchel and pull out a tiny clay vessel filled with explosive flash powder, and hurl it at a point on the ground within 30 feet of you. The pot explodes on impact, producing a bright flash. Each creature within ten feet of the point of impact must succed on a Constitution saving throw or become &amp;Reference[blinded], &amp;Reference[dazed], and &amp;Reference[deafened] until the end of your next turn.</p>",
